
Installing and Running KToon 2D Animation Toolkit

Before you begin, you need Qt version 4.1.1 or later to be installed.

Package
	First, download the source tarball from http://ktoon.toonka.com/.
	
	Unpack it into your desired location and go into the uncompressed directory
	
	Running the configure and build script
	  $ ./configure [--enable-ktoonstyle] [--enable-kinas]
	  $ ./build.sh --prefix [prefix]
	

For translate ktoon
	$ cd scripts
	$ sh translate.sh

-- The KToon Team

